{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "第五回凌风公子。剑客行故事继续。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但是，她究竟又是什么人物呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小可……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管你是谁，快给我滚出去!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道我是谁?你知不知这是什么地方?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人是谁?这是什么地方?难道他就是这里的主人?那么那高贵的妇人，怎会将我带到这里来而他却不知道?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你受了伤，那么，又是谁将你带来此地的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下是否此地的主人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是此地的主人，哼哼，难道你是此地的主人不成!",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "惭愧!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小可实在不知此处是何地，也不知是怎么来的?阁下若是此地的主人，只管将小可抬出去便是，唉!小可……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不知道这是什么地方?也不知道是怎么来的?哼哼!",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管你有伤无伤，有病无病，快些给我滚出去，若是等到我亲自出手，哼哼，那你就惨了!",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下若是此地的主人，小可自应离去，只是小可此来，实非出于本意，阁下又何苦如此咄咄逼人!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一盏茶之内，你若不快些滚出去，本公子立时便让你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此说来，你若未病，我就无法伤你了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个亦未可知。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展白呀展白，你宁可被这少年摔出房去，也万万不可连累人家!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这少年本来立即叫我离开这里，怎地微微把了我的脉，就一言不发地转身走了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我此刻周身并不痛苦，却又没有一丝力气，这些天来，我失去知觉，理应病得不轻，但此刻我怎的连一点病后那种难受的感觉都没有?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人是谁?居然在我床上高卧起来，你们虽然都养尊处优惯了，等闲不会轻易动弹一下，但却不致一个个连眼睛都瞎了吧?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么同样是人，有些人却如此可怜?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这少年年纪轻轻，怎地就如此目中无人，做出一副盛气凌人的样子来?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这怎怪得人家?若是有个不相识的人高卧在我的床上，我又当如何呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "站住!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你来干什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人是谁?怎地这四条彪形健壮的汉子，竟会对她如此恭谨?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道她就是那神秘而高贵的中年美妇?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些人到底是什么身份?这地方究竟是什么地方?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是武林世家?抑或是豪富巨宅?甚或是公侯府邸呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "站住!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们方才在干什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎地又是这种腔调!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才公子爷吩咐小的们将这位相公抬出去，是以——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们倒听话得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你叫他们把人家抬出去的吗?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要你来管什闲事，难道我叫人将一个不相识的人从我床上抬走，与你又有什么干系不成?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "亏你还算是武林中久以聪明智计著名的人物!哼，我看你的脑筋，倒也有限得很，你难道不会想一想，这少年若是没有来历，又怎会跑到这里来养伤?难道家里的人都死了不成?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看你们还是死了好了，像你们这样半死不活的样子，哼哼，真是——",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你在说谁?可要说清楚些!",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你如此紧张作甚?难道我说的是你?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你现在是武林中成名露脸的大英雄，大豪杰了，怎会把我这个姐姐放在眼里?可是——哼，难道连妈妈也都不在你眼下了吗?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊!这陌生少年，难道是她老人家送到我这里来养伤的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她为什么会露出那种忧郁的神态?按理说，她不该如此忧郁的呀!她言语之中，像是对自己的儿子失望得很，却又是为着什么呢?如今她的儿子不仅年轻英俊，并且又在武林中享有盛名，而我呢……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若不是她老人家，还有谁敢把人带人你这房……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方才那刹那之间，难道她已在这四条大汉的面颊之上，各各击了两掌?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可知道他们是谁的手下?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他虽是初人江湖，但",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    }
  ],
